A sudden attack
After the lizards became hostile to humans, a skirmish should have happened between them. Now it is necessary to attack the human camp while they are weakened.
#subobj 1
Come to the meeting place
Orc warriors have already taken position not far from the human camp. At first you need to conduct a diversion in the camp, reducing the number of defenders. A frontal attack will most likely fail, the camp is still well protected.
#subobj 2
Knock people out of the camp
This camp was built by orcs and it should belong to them!